data.description: Spacious detached townhome has been well taken care of by same owner since 2010. This home has not been smoked in or had any pets. Home is located in the development called Fairway crossings and has the Ponds golf course next to it. Some features of interest of this home are: main level primary bedroom with walk-in closet as well as private bath with jetted tub. The main level also features a four season porch with a gas fireplace as well as access to the private deck. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances as well as updated laminate floor. The lower level features an office that has a nice sized walk-in closet. For the last 13 years, there has only been one person living here, so it has been gently used. The insulated garage (24x20) has nice cabinets, water faucet, gas line for future heater, as well as an epoxy floor: very clean and sharp looking. Poured concrete edging has been added. Have your morning coffee off the front porch, or the back deck; you have options!
